## Wrong
### 1. Wrong Path
see https://github.com/flutter/flutter-intellij/blob/master/CONTRIBUTING.md  -> Provision Tool

![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/20944001/131302672-a142b567-ec88-4992-80ab-77e005beb5be.png)

【/bin/plugin】This path will visit system root. It should be【bin/plugin】

### 2. Can't find version 

![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/20944001/131336652-a7c008fa-3b8e-4a8c-a134-93482264bb8d.png)

【Adding platform sources】said 【Sync to the same version as in lib/dart-plugin】. 
dart-plugin version in master is **203.6912**. And this version can't find in https://github.com/JetBrains/intellij-plugins

## Misunderstanding
### 1. The Flutter version is not described in the documentation
Because of the null safety, dart require '>=2.12.0 <3.0.0'.  So, it is best to specify the required Flutter version in the documentation

### 2. There is a problem with the order

![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/20944001/131337450-2427ae26-126c-4f21-9224-21b32e186ead.png)

The order of these two steps should be swapped, because [dart pub get] need to before [dart tool/plugin/bin/main.dart].
